{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:30:21.964820+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "灰石镇的中央广场上，石砌房屋环绕，镇长艾德温正站在市政厅门前，神情凝重地望着远方。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "旅人，欢迎来到灰石镇。我是镇长艾德温。近来边境异象频发，人心惶惶。你既已至此，可愿助我查明真相？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与镇长艾德温对话，艾德温提出请求调查边境异象。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:world_bible:-:-:-:4f2f19ba", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:location:-:loc_001:-:641609fd", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:76a89601"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 14}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:30:43.459511+00:00", "player_text": "我愿意", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "艾德温听到你的答复，神情略显宽慰，但仍带着谨慎。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "感谢你的应允，旅人。灰石镇近来不安宁——黑松林传出异响，月影湖水色浑浊，连北境要塞也中断了例行通报。我已将三件关键任务分别托付给镇外的几位可信赖之人：德鲁伊学徒瑟琳娜、渔女伊芙琳与要塞指挥官卡洛斯。若你能完成他们的委托，带回德鲁伊橡木徽章、月影湖净水瓶与要塞军令符，或许能揭开这笼罩王国的阴影。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "main_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": null, "objective": null, "guidance": "前往黑松林、月影湖或铁脊山隘，分别接触瑟琳娜、伊芙琳或卡洛斯以推进任务。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家同意协助镇长调查边境异象，艾德温说明了三项支线委托及其对应的关键道具。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:world_bible:-:-:-:4f2f19ba", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:location:-:loc_001:-:641609fd", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:76a89601", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b37846c5", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:summary:-:-:1:71a1be7a"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 15}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "turn_index": 3, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:31:03.762415+00:00", "player_text": "收到", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "艾德温站在市政厅门前，目光沉稳地注视着你，似乎在确认你的决心。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "很好，旅人。你可先在镇上准备些必需品——我听说草药师莉安娜手头有净水晶瓶和银鳞鱼尾，或许能帮你在月影湖的任务中省些力气。若你已备妥行装，黑松林与铁脊山隘皆可通行。愿圣光护佑你的前路。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "艾德温建议玩家向草药师莉安娜购买任务所需物品，并提示可前往黑松林或铁脊山隘。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:world_bible:-:-:-:4f2f19ba", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:location:-:loc_001:-:641609fd", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:76a89601", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b37846c5", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:23ab7df4", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:summary:-:-:1:71a1be7a", "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a:summary:-:-:2:86ca20c8"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_092818_a1ef4c1a", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 16}}}
